---
import MainLayout from "@/layouts/MainLayout";

import Container from "@/components/layout/Container";
import Review from "@/components/content/Review";
import Section from "@/components/layout/Section";
import Service from "@/components/content/Service";
---

<MainLayout>
    <div class="bg-mongoose-900 md:bg-radial-[at_90%_60%] to-mongoose-950 from-mongoose-300 space-y-8 lg:space-y-12">
        <Section>
            <Container>
                <h1 class="text-white text-balance">Powersport Repair and Service Rates</h1>

                <div class="text-mongoose-100 text-xl md:text-2xl space-y-6 tracking -tight leading-normal font-light max-w-5xl mt-12">
                    <p>
                        We believe in complete honesty and transparency when it comes to service costs. At Dripping Springs Outdoor Powersports, you will never encounter hidden fees or surprise charges. We are committed to being upfront about our competitive labor rate and the total cost of your
                        repair or service.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 mt-12 md:ml-12">
                    <div class="flex flex-col">
                        <div class="h5 text-mongoose-200!">Service Rate</div>
                        <div class="h2">$85.00 per service</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex flex-col">
                        <div class="h5 text-mongoose-200!">Labor Rate</div>
                        <div class="h2">$125.00 per hour</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="text-mongoose-100 text-lg space-y-6 tracking-normal max-w-4xl mt-12">
                    <p>
                        Your total repair cost is calculated by combining our Service Fee and the Hourly Labor Rate. The Service Fee is a flat charge that covers the cost of all trips and logistical coordination related to your original service visitâ€”whether it involves initial diagnostics, a return
                        trip to install parts, or final testing.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Our competitive Hourly Labor Rate is then applied only to the actual time our certified technician spends working on your equipment. Any necessary replacement parts, such as filters, fluids, or major components, are charged separately at their wholesale cost plus a small
                        markup. This ensures you know exactly what you are paying for: trip coverage, hands-on expertise, and necessary parts.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </Container>

            <div>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-4 sm:grid-cols-8 sm:w-[125vw] sm:-translate-x-40 gap-4">
                    <img src="https://imgix.cosmicjs.com/bdc03c70-d062-11f0-9412-e12f763e1300-side-view-man-repairing-motorcycle.jpg?w=700" class="shadow-2xl w-full h-30 sm:h-60 object-cover col-span-2" />
                    <img src="https://imgix.cosmicjs.com/bdc03c70-d062-11f0-9412-e12f763e1300-side-view-man-repairing-motorcycle.jpg?w=700" class="shadow-2xl w-full h-30 sm:h-60 object-cover col-span-2" />
                    <img src="https://imgix.cosmicjs.com/bdc03c70-d062-11f0-9412-e12f763e1300-side-view-man-repairing-motorcycle.jpg?w=700" class="shadow-2xl w-full h-30 sm:h-60 object-cover col-span-2" />
                    <img src="https://imgix.cosmicjs.com/bdc03c70-d062-11f0-9412-e12f763e1300-side-view-man-repairing-motorcycle.jpg?w=700" class="shadow-2xl w-full h-30 sm:h-60 object-cover col-span-2" />
                </div>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-8 sm:w-[125vw] sm:-translate-x-10 gap-4 mt-4">
                    <img src="https://imgix.cosmicjs.com/bdc03c70-d062-11f0-9412-e12f763e1300-side-view-man-repairing-motorcycle.jpg?w=700" class="shadow-2xl w-full h-25 sm:h-60 object-cover col-span-2" />
                    <img src="https://imgix.cosmicjs.com/bdc03c70-d062-11f0-9412-e12f763e1300-side-view-man-repairing-motorcycle.jpg?w=700" class="shadow-2xl w-full h-25 sm:h-60 object-cover col-span-2" />
                    <img src="https://imgix.cosmicjs.com/bdc03c70-d062-11f0-9412-e12f763e1300-side-view-man-repairing-motorcycle.jpg?w=700" class="shadow-2xl w-full h-25 sm:h-60 object-cover col-span-2" />
                    <img src="https://imgix.cosmicjs.com/bdc03c70-d062-11f0-9412-e12f763e1300-side-view-man-repairing-motorcycle.jpg?w=700" class="shadow-2xl w-full h-25 sm:h-60 object-cover col-span-2" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </Section>
    </div>
</MainLayout>
